examples.en: They strung wires from tree to tree.
The jewels are strung together on a fine silver chain.
Try not to get too strung up before the examination, it doesn't help.
People like that should be strung up from the nearest tree.
We strung popcorn garlands for the Christmas tree.
Christmas lights were strung from one end of Main Street to the other.
He set a row of posts in the ground and strung barbwire between them.
